  "title": "Clinic Assistant (Office Hours)",
  "description": "<h4>Job Description</h4>\n<p><u><strong>Perform department operations</strong></u></p>\n<p>Administer clinic's appointment resources and slots management</p>\n<p>Manage frontline and assist second tier escalation in patient management</p>\n<p>Order, Monitor and maintain inventories of clinical non-clinical items</p>\n<p>Arranges for prescribed laboratory tests, specialist referrals and/or any other procedures</p>\n<p>Reconcile daily monetary transactions</p>\n<p>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Provide clinical support</strong></u></p>\n<p>Assist doctors during the treatment and examination of patients</p>\n<p>Perform basic clinical procedures</p>\n<p>Perform measurement of basic health parameters</p>\n<p>Prepare consultation rooms</p>\n<p>Prepare patients for physical examination or minor procedures to be performed by doctors</p>\n<p>Prepare patients' records and documentation pre- and post- consultation and procedures</p>\n<p>Provide patient and caregiver education when necessary</p>\n<p><u><strong>Provide frontline services</strong></u></p>\n<p>ldentify situations where patients require additional attention</p>\n<p>Manage patients' feedback and enquiries</p>\n<p>Perform patient registration and discharge: Receive, screen and register patients into the clinical system</p>\n<p>Perform payment collection procedures: Obtains and verifies patient billing information before collecting payment</p>\n<p>Promote use of automated or self-help services</p>\n<p>Provide financial counselling to patients</p>\n<p>Schedule appointments for patients</p>",
